    {
      "instruction": "<p>Tear your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the<strong> torn ciabatta</strong> to a baking tray with your <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until golden and crisp – these are your<strong> sesame croutons</strong></p>",
