    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>,<strong> rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> to a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>hoisin</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
